'''單寫多讀'''（或称“單次寫多次讀”，{{lang-en|'''Write once read many'''}}）簡稱為'''WORM'''，是指[[儲存裝置|儲存裝置]]一旦錄寫後便不能修改，當中又先後有[[CD-R|CD-R]]和[[DVD-R|DVD-R]]發明<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.computerhistory.org/collections/accession/102671161 |title=IBM 3363 Optical WORM drive |accessdate=2016-04-24 |archive-date=2013-06-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130613222944/http://www.computerhistory.org/collections/accession/102671161 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。這類設備常被用在{{link-en|美國金融業監管局|Financial Industry Regulatory Authority}}和[[美國證券交易委員會|美國證券交易委員會]]等{{link-en|經紀自營商|Broker-dealer}}的紀錄上<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://mitchatkinsfinrabrokerdealerconsulting.com/back-to-basics-an-old-rule-in-a-new-world/ |title="Back to Basics – An Old Rule in a New World" |accessdate=2016-04-24 |archive-date=2019-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190924002055/http://mitchatkinsfinrabrokerdealerconsulting.com/back-to-basics-an-old-rule-in-a-new-world/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

